<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ثَبَتُ المَرَاجِع<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#950000">" القُرْانُ الكَرِيمِ"</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - <span style="color:#950000">"أخْلاقُ العُلَمَاءِ"</span> للآجُرِّي.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢ - <span style="color:#950000">"الزُّهْدُ"</span> لأحْمَدَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣ - <span style="color:#950000">"أدَبُ الدُّنْيا والدِّينِ"</span> للمَاوَرْدِيِّ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٤ - <span style="color:#950000">"اقْتِضاءُ الصِّرَاطِ المُسْتَقِيمِ"</span> لابنِ تَيمِيَّةَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٥ - <span style="color:#950000">"اقْتِضاءُ العِلْمِ العَمَلَ"</span> للخَطِيبِ البَغْدَادِيِّ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٦ - <span style="color:#950000">"الآدَابُ الشَّرْعِيَّةُ"</span> لابنِ مُفْلِحٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٧ - <span style="color:#950000">"البِدَايَةُ والنِّهَايَةُ"</span> لابنِ كَثِيرٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٨ - <span style="color:#950000">"البَرْمَجة اللُّغَوِيَّةُ العَصَبِيَّةُ"</span> لأحْمَدَ الزَّهْرَانِيِّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٩ - <span style="color:#950000">"الجامِعُ لآدَابِ الرَّاوي"</span> للخَطِيبِ البَغْدَادِيِّ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١٠ - <span style="color:#950000">"الجَلِيسُ الصَّالِحُ"</span> لسِبْطِ ابنِ الجَوْزِيِّ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١١ - <span style="color:#950000">"الحِلْيَةُ"</span> لأبِي نُعَيمٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>١٢ - <span style="color:#950000">"الزُّهْدُ"</span> للحَسَنِ البَصْرِيِّ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١٣ - <span style="color:#950000">"السِّلْسِلَةُ الصَّحِيحَةُ"</span> للألْبَانِيِّ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>